thread.title_full: BRIEF-Simple H1 net result turns to loss of 685,000 zlotys | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Simple H1 net result turns to loss of 685,000 zlotys
text:
Sept 1 Simple SA :
* Said on Monday that it reported H1 revenue of 24.8 million zlotys ($6.6 million) versus 23.8 million zlotys a year ago
* H1 operating loss of 1.2 mln zlotys versus profit of 1.9 mln zlotys a year ago
* H1 net loss of 685,000 zlotys versus profit of 1.8 mln zlotys a year ago
